title: 110 Delicious Dessert Icons 2D Food Art Pack, Transparent Background
description: 110 unique and mouth-watering 2D dessert icons, perfect for adding a delicious visual element to any scene.
longDescription:
Add a Sweet Touch to Your Game with 110 Colorful Dessert Icons!

Looking for vibrant, high-quality food icons to enhance your game or project? This pack offers 110 unique and mouth-watering 2D dessert icons, perfect for adding a delicious visual element to any scene. Whether you're developing a mobile game, a restaurant management sim, or a fun casual app, these icons will make your project stand out!


Key Features:

  • 110 Unique Icons: A diverse collection of colorful desserts, including cakes, cheesecakes, ice cream, pastries, and more.
  • High Resolution: Each icon is rendered at 1024x1024 pixels, ensuring crisp and clear visuals on any device or screen size.
  • Transparent Background: All icons are delivered in PNG format with transparent backgrounds, making them easy to integrate into any scene or UI.
  • Versatile Usage: Perfect for a variety of projects such as games, apps, websites, or promotional materials. Ideal for genres like casual, puzzle, simulation, or educational games.
  • Easy Integration: The icons are ready to use, and the transparent background ensures you can effortlessly drag and drop them into your project without any additional editing.

File Details:

  • Format: PNG
  • Resolution: 1024x1024 pixels
  • Transparent Background: Yes
  • Total Icons: 110 unique icons

Why Choose This Pack?

This icon pack is designed for maximum flexibility, offering high-quality food art that can enhance gameplay, UI design, and visual storytelling. Whether you're building a dessert shop game, a cooking app, or simply adding fun icons to your project, this pack makes the process easy and enjoyable.


Support and Updates:

This is the first version of the pack, and updates will be made based on user feedback. Your satisfaction is our priority, and we are committed to improving and expanding this asset over time. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out at olgabutymova27@gmail.com.

We value your feedback! Please consider leaving a rating and review to help us make this pack even better for future updates.
